== Nolosha shaqsiga ah ==
Silk Smitha wuxuu lahaa wareeg yar oo saaxiibo dhow ah. Waxay ahayd qof isdaba-joog ah oo aan si dhakhso leh ula saaxiibin qof. Waxay sidoo kale caan ku tahay dabacsanaan, xoog iyo toosnaan, taas oo dadka qaar ku khaldeen inay nasiib wanaag tahay. Waxay caan ku ahayd inay timaado goobta lagu duubayay filimka kahor toogashada, iyadu iyadu mas'uul bay ahayd, waxayna hami haysay (waxay baratay inay si wanaagsan ugu hadasho Ingiriisiga inkasta oo waxbarashadeeda ay aad uyartahay). Saaxiibbadeed waxay ku sifeeyeen inay leedahay "jilicsan" iyo "ilmo sida" shakhsiyad. Waxay ku xariifsanayd [[Weji qurxis|qurxinta]] taas oo ahayd shaqadeeda kahor intaysan atariisho noqon.<ref>[https://www.news18.com/amp/news/movies/silk-smitha-birth-anniversary-five-most-memorable-performances-of-the-actress-3136643.html "Silk Smitha Birth Anniversary: Five Most Memorable Performances of the Actress"]. ''News18''.</ref> Waxay si dabiici ah u qurux badneyd oo caan ku aheyd indhaheeda quruxda badan, midabkeeda dahabka iyo jir ahaanba.<ref>[https://filmfare.com/features/silk-smithas-bold-interview-4813.amp "Silk Smitha's bold interview"]{{Dead link|date=August 2021 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}. ''Filmfare''.</ref><ref>[https://www.dtnext.in/News/Cinema/2020/09/23182151/1252693/Remembering-Silk-Smitha-on-her-24th-death-anniversary.vpf "Remembering Silk Smitha on her 24th death anniversary"].</ref>

== Dhimasho ==
Subaxnimadii Sebtember 23, 1996, waxay la xiriirtay saaxiibkeed, qoob-ka-ciyaarka Anuradha, si ay ugala hadlaan arrin iyada qasan.  Anuradha waxay qorsheysay inay soo booqato ka dib markay ilmaheeda ku dhaaftay dugsiga.

Imaanshaha dambe ee subaxdaas, Anuradha waxay aragtay Smitha oo meyd ah.  Dhowr bilood ka dib dhimashadeeda, waxaa lagu caddeeyay warbixinta dhimashada ka dib in Smitha ay u dhimatay ismiidaamin, iyadoo qamri badan uu ku jiray jirkeeda.<ref>[https://web.archive.org/web/20131221172406/http://cinema.maalaimalar.com/2013/12/16224107/cinema-history.html "'சுமிதாவுக்கு திருமணத்தில் நம்பிக்கை இல்லை': 'சில்க்' சுமிதாவின் காதலர் பேட்டி"]. ''Cinema.maalaimalar.com''.</ref><ref>[https://web.archive.org/web/20140114224641/http://cinema.maalaimalar.com/2013/12/15203008/Silk-smitha-cinema-history.html "'எனக்கு வாழ்க்கை தருவதாக"]. </ref>

